title: Chanel Kelly Top Handle Bag
description: Chanel Kelly top handle bag in black diamond-quilted caviar leather (7xxxxxx, circa: 2002-2003). Featuring gold-toned hardware, single top leather handle, and rear exterior patch pocket. The classic CC turn-lock closure opens to a black smooth leather interior with patch pocket and a zip pocket. Approximate dimensions: 29cm(Base-L) x 24cm(H) x 12cm(D), handle drop 8cm. Accompanied by a Chanel authentication card. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned).
